channel.title: Comments on: Blake Schwarzenbach returns with Thorns Of Life

item.title: By: Trey
item.dc:creator: Trey
item.description: Stange, I just listened to 24 Hour Revenge Therapy in its entirety Monday night, something I probably haven't done since the WUSC days.
item.content:encoded: Stange, I just listened to 24 Hour Revenge Therapy in its entirety Monday night, something I probably haven’t done since the WUSC days.

item.title: By: Michael M.
item.dc:creator: Michael M.
item.description: Oh, everything up through 24 Hour Revenge Therapy still sounds classic (and good) to me. I'm just not sure if new songs of that type will hit the 34-year-old me in quite the same way that the early albums hit the 18-20 year old me.
item.content:encoded: Oh, everything up through 24 Hour Revenge Therapy still sounds classic (and good) to me. I’m just not sure if new songs of that type will hit the 34-year-old me in quite the same way that the early albums hit the 18-20 year old me.

item.title: By: Eric Greenwood
item.dc:creator: Eric Greenwood
item.description: @ Michael M. i don't know..."Want" still sounds like a classic song to me.
item.content:encoded: @ Michael M. i don’t know…”Want” still sounds like a classic song to me.
